function_call.name: generate_sql_schema_with_tree
function_call.arguments: {"prompt":"Design a SQL database schema for a Clinic Management Software with the following modules: Appointments & Queue Management, Patient Records & EMR, E-Prescription, Billing & Payments, Patient Engagement, Reports & Analytics, Teleconsultation, AI Features, Pharmacy & Lab integration. Include tables for users (doctors, staff, patients), appointments, patient records, prescriptions, billing, payments, reminders, reports, teleconsultations, pharmacy, lab reports, AI logs, and subscription plans. Capture free vs paid module access. Show relationships between tables. Use postgres dialect. Include constraints and build a tree for visualization.","dialect":"postgres","includeConstraints":true,"buildTree":true}
